data.description: Get the best of both worlds in this stunning 4/2 pool home in highly sought after Lake Como neighborhood! Step onto the corner lot (with  beautiful circular paver driveway) and enjoy the peace and serenity in your fenced in yard, or take a dip in your sparkling pool! Enjoy access to  plenty of greenspace and lakes, shopping, entertainment, and some of the best dining in Orlando, as downtown is just moments away! The home  is designed for creating memories with a layout that provides both easy flow and quiet separation. Master suite sits apart from the other  bedrooms, creating your own oasis. Ductwork completely replaced in July 2023. Plumbing and wiring have been updated, and NEW ROOF all give you peace of mind for many years. Cinch  home warranty will give you added comfort! NO HOA means you can add your own personal touches! Homes in this neighborhood do not last  long, so don't miss your shot at your new forever home, and make an appointment today!
